Package: mediamtx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser
Description: Real-time media server and network video recorder
 MediaMTX NVR is a production-grade media server with built-in NVR
 capabilities. It supports RTSP, RTMP, HLS, WebRTC, and SRT protocols
 with ONVIF camera integration, SQLite-backed recording management,
 and a web-based administration interface.
 .
 Features include:
  - Multi-protocol streaming (RTSP, RTMP, HLS, WebRTC, SRT)
  - ONVIF camera auto-discovery and management
  - Continuous and event-triggered recording
  - Web-based admin console
  - RESTful API for integration
